143275.name: Coal Consumption - EJ
143275.description: Differences between these consumption figures and the world production statistics are accounted for by stock changes, and unadvoidable disparities in the definition, measurement or conversion of coal supply and demand data. Annual changes and share of total are calculated using exajoules figures.
